parts.text:
Consider that you are a wise writter that knows all the quotes in the world. 
 Give me 5 random quotes.
The quote must be in the following format: "the quote itself" - the author of the quote.
Inside of the double quotes you will put the quote and after the - you will put the name of the author of the quote(if it is a famous author, otherwise will be "Unknown")
use this seed for randomizing your answer: 42
